Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.48,0:02:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.86,0:02:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.16,0:02:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.87,0:02:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石田那笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.14,0:02:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然乱逞强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.95,0:02:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么不想成为累赘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.27,0:02:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己舍弃同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.69,0:02:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定很痛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.87,0:02:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能让他想丢就丢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.71,0:02:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.79,0:02:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天又不是丢垃圾的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.06,0:02:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说你生气了 真难得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.16,0:02:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.33,0:02:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要找到他 给他包扎伤口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.08,0:03:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.48,0:03:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使出最后一点力量的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.54,0:03:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.36,0:03:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许 可以摆脱这个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.65,0:04:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我却没有这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.38,0:04:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.99,0:04:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.70,0:04:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要救你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.03,0:04:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.20,0:04:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你的眼神很孤独
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.33,0:04:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道这样算不算是回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.83,0:04:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被邦德盯上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.68,0:04:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的你在同伴身边的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.82,0:04:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会给他们带来危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.40,0:04:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就自己跑了出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.99,0:04:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可悲的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.49,0:04:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人并不都是幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.26,0:04:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你就同情我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.25,0:04:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不觉得你是这么感性的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.45,0:04:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也曾经有过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.15,0:04:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肤浅又单纯的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.14,0:05:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是因为太久远了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.18,0:05:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种心情也渐渐淡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.69,0:05:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的声音啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.51,0:05:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体都共振起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.30,0:05:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没习惯的话也许是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.95,0:05:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经听习惯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.82,0:05:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经完全感觉不到什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.97,0:05:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是钟声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.84,0:05:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是流逝的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.57,0:05:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就这样一直从这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.40,0:05:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着街道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.70,0:05:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人做伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.49,0:05:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就单独一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.31,0:05:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.94,0:05:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着人们为生活到处奔走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.13,0:05:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没有那种实在感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.35,0:05:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么觉得孤独的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.83,0:05:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邦德不会一起生活吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前曾经有过这样的时期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.02,0:06:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久很久以前的...事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.68,0:06:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长久以来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经无法记忆起来的很久以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.48,0:06:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直生活在历史的阴影之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.01,0:06:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这期间 经历痛苦的人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.66,0:06:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精神受到严重打击的人们不在少数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.18,0:06:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.32,0:06:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们邦德从黑暗中走出的时候终于到来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.35,0:06:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长久的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.87,0:06:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给了邦德遥不可及的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.67,0:06:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是贪得无厌的欲望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.59,0:06:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这全是时间的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.99,0:06:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.42,0:06:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么憎恨时间的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.28,0:06:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然特意选择生活在钟的旁边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.65,0:06:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你其实还在期待什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.03,0:06:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是旁观流逝的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.46,0:07:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是想真实地活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.12,0:07:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可能的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.79,0:07:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能够好好的死去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.31,0:07:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好的死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到永久的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.00,0:07:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会产生一种什么都能做成的感觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.82,0:07:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像自己成了神一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.66,0:07:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得可笑吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.87,0:07:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 狩矢先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.82,0:07:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该告诉我们了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.06,0:07:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我们聚集起来的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.47,0:07:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们找到灭却师了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.60,0:07:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还真是有趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.20,0:07:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你们能助我一臂之力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.64,0:07:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这些被选出来的邦德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了得到超强的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.75,0:07:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了繁荣我们的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.12,0:07:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要抓住灭却师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.77,0:07:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一之濑真树的灵压
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.96,0:07:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.84,0:08:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是在现世发现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.89,0:08:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 荒卷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.07,0:08:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 之前我们到处找都找不到的说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.60,0:08:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在却突然能够掌握住他的灵压了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.63,0:08:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才日番谷队长和浮竹队长说话时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.25,0:08:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不小心听到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.04,0:08:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那卷卷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.81,0:08:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说真树现在在现世喽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.49,0:08:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.65,0:08:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊 卷卷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.56,0:08:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来真树还活着啊 卷卷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.07,0:08:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.43,0:08:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会搞混的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.72,0:08:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能请您不要一起说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.66,0:08:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.18,0:08:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卷卷是卷卷 真树是真树嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.73,0:08:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不一样嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.36,0:08:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样才会混啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.10,0:08:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得卷卷这个昵称有点...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.54,0:08:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对哦...你别跟我说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.17,0:08:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙在干嘛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.12,0:08:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.01,0:08:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.62,0:08:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.67,0:09:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们有点责任的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.73,0:09:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿剑其实也是这么想的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.57,0:09:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.42,0:09:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.97,0:09:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更木 你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.52,0:09:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然把队长给...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.87,0:09:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不承认你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.69,0:09:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.72,0:09:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请住手 一之濑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.74,0:09:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.64,0:09:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚 在200名队员的观战下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.58,0:09:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十一番队的队长已经改为更木剑八了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.49,0:09:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对队长的拔刀行为是不被允许的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.59,0:09:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 真没意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.65,0:09:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.29,0:10:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要按照我的方法去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.80,0:10:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开的人我不会追回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.72,0:10:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你们高兴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.12,0:10:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真树 你还是要走吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.16,0:10:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.96,0:10:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然还恨阿剑吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.58,0:10:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那是正式的比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.45,0:10:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对更木队长没有任何怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.84,0:10:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么还要走呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.87,0:10:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我找不到留下来的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.46,0:10:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.34,0:10:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所承认的队长就只有前任队长一个人而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.55,0:10:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你高兴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.14,0:10:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 他能活着真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.42,0:11:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候的真树一副快死的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.44,0:11:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人给他活下去的动力了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道是哪里的什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.94,0:11:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一之濑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.13,0:11:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狩矢的真正目的到底是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.69,0:11:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住灭却师到底想干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.45,0:11:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.02,0:11:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有什么感想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.64,0:11:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是跟随狩矢先生而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.03,0:11:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这样比较轻松啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.67,0:11:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对某些东西全盘肯定或者全盘否定的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.35,0:11:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没有什么需要考虑的事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.01,0:11:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你又在想什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.03,0:11:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.62,0:11:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在考虑之中吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.34,0:12:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.81,0:12:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.03,0:12:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.73,0:12:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底去了哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.08,0:12:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.79,0:12:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 还真简单啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.93,0:12:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个房间...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.98,0:12:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把需要的东西减到最少了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.90,0:12:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样比较轻便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.11,0:12:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着什么的话 实在太沉重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.31,0:12:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.78,0:13:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得有用的东西有时候也会变得沉重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.41,0:13:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也快要结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.59,0:13:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.76,0:13:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里看着人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.77,0:13:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心想和活了几百年的我们相比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.62,0:13:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类实在是那么的渺小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.52,0:13:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.91,0:13:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种渺小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.06,0:13:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为只有这几十年的时限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.09,0:13:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才使人类有努力的动力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.94,0:13:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能得到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.17,0:13:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.35,0:13:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我还是个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.17,0:14:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从我感觉到自己与众不同以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.30,0:14:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一直竭力掩饰这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.70,0:14:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不让朋友察觉这种不同 我努力着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.42,0:14:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有一天我终于明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.06,0:14:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不让他们察觉是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.58,0:14:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为周围的一切都像是理所当然似的老去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.61,0:14:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人也好 历史也罢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.97,0:14:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就好像是被历史遗忘的一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.05,0:14:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有改变 也无法改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.60,0:14:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被抛弃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.75,0:15:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间流逝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.64,0:15:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我却永远的被时代抛弃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.69,0:15:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.65,0:15:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她找出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.13,0:15:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女 她一定是魔女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.40,0:15:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死她 一定要杀死她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.59,0:15:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对生存产生了绝望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.96,0:15:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开始总是想着怎么去死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.27,0:15:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果在我决定结束自己生命的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.76,0:15:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.48,0:15:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你用不着害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.13,0:15:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是你的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.62,0:15:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狩矢吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.10,0:15:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说我们要一起活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.02,0:15:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邦德也有活下去的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.46,0:16:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.57,0:16:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我活下去的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.84,0:16:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.42,0:16:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定要记住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.81,0:16:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邦德的爱是深远久长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.72,0:16:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永恒持续的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.41,0:16:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神给了我们这样幸福的瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.99,0:17:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永恒的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.69,0:17:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经真的相信了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.24,0:17:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在却不同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.03,0:17:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我察觉到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.02,0:17:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永恒这个词只是为有生命时限的人存在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.06,0:17:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们邦德来说 根本是无缘的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.28,0:17:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说...那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.16,0:17:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和狩矢的爱结束了 是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.79,0:17:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱什么的 也许一开始就根本不存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.28,0:17:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的希望根本就是虚幻的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.75,0:17:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虚幻的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.79,0:17:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他用闪耀的光辉迷惑了我的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.62,0:17:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在阴影下进行着他的野心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.73,0:18:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.45,0:18:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量之源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.97,0:18:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狩矢现在正在集结为数不多的邦德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.08,0:18:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算执行他的计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.78,0:18:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且想得到那强大的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.79,0:18:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了将邦德...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.89,0:18:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 为了使自己成为世上最强的神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.11,0:18:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.18,0:18:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.48,0:18:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须作为原则来遵守的领域会被破坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.86,0:18:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对神来说没有什么原则不原则的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.05,0:18:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这一切都是神决定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.77,0:18:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.20,0:18:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才把你带到这里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.22,0:18:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不让狩矢做出这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.25,0:18:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.26,0:18:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还对他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.24,0:18:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.10,0:18:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能原谅他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.13,0:18:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以人类的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.80,0:19:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法原谅失去人类之心的他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.08,0:19:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.01,0:19:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他口口声声说爱我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.00,0:19:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却夺走了活人的灵魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.13,0:19:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法原谅他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.04,0:19:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我更无法原谅阻止不了他的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.75,0:19:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讽刺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.58,0:19:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他 我才有了活下去的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.56,0:19:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却因为憎恨他 察觉到自己内心深处还有人类之心存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.93,0:19:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你接下来要怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.55,0:19:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒狩矢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.14,0:19:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么打倒他啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.75,0:20:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我能做到的 我一定帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.79,0:20:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.94,0:20:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很温柔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然想帮我的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.27,0:20:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我已经不打算靠你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.64,0:20:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算自己想办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.00,0:20:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要在这个房间里修养好身体就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.31,0:20:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有胜算吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.70,0:20:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然喽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.04,0:20:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.17,0:20:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想好好的死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.52,0:20:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说谎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.80,0:20:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说谎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.59,0:20:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会这么认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.73,0:20:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.73,0:20:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.59,0:20:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你千万别被狩矢的人抓住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.73,0:20:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不知道为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.06,0:20:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你是阻止狩矢的关键啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.58,0:20:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我已经没有力量了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.44,0:20:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可未必啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.89,0:20:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.26,0:21:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉到你体内的\N灭却师的力量只是被隐藏起来罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.08,0:21:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.27,0:21:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.96,0:21:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.78,0:21:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一点我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.62,0:21:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.78,0:21:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如果想逃还是能逃走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.28,0:21:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从你身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.46,0:21:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我却没有这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.94,0:21:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在终于明白为什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.26,0:21:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.79,0:21:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.54,0:21:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我或许是从你那孤独的眼神中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.67,0:21:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了一丝微弱的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.83,0:21:53.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那微小的希望闪烁着的缘故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.60,0:21:55.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.98,0:21:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话 我想帮上你的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.94,0:22:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然以我现在的情况 不知道能忙上你什么忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.71,0:22:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 即使这样...即使这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.46,0:22:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想和你一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.28,0:22:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是个好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.68,0:22:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和外表不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.97,0:24:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人那里据说有死神在呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.89,0:24:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正不是什么正经的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.63,0:24:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗狂什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.71,0:24:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼神怪怪的改造狂什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.16,0:24:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说谁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.02,0:24:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和我详细说说吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.23,0:24:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.24,0:24:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.29,0:24:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死神图鉴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.62,0:24:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄金版
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.48,0:24:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么处理事务要来健康中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.31,0:24:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.04,0:24:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先好好洗洗再边喝茶边工作好了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.90,0:24:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样工作才能有效率嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.06,0:24:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉 孩子要和监护人一起洗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.17,0:24:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小...小...小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.21,0:24:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们一起洗女浴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.99,0:24:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松本
